To use this application on anything, make sure you have python installed on your computer. Then open the terminal/command line/shell, in the command line, type cd and drag the folder into the terminal and hit enter. type python3 devicehack.py and press enter. The python script should start running in the command line.

DISCLAIMER: THIS IS A PRANK. This will not hack anything.
 Works best when you use this with green terminal text and use it to start a tv cast with a laptop.